{"tid":1980570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"渣打銀行宣布將助劏房戶交租，名額2000，每戶5000元","createTime":"2020-04-20T07:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T08:09:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7246eefaf03f6cba08cb289b415d3ac694117937","tid":1980570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1750878/即時-港聞-周四起申請-渣打助劏房戶交租-名額2000每戶5000元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1750878%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%8A%A9%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E4%BA%A4%E7%A7%9F-%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D2000%E6%AF%8F%E6%88%B65000%E5%85%83&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=49c227c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1750878%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%8A%A9%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E4%BA%A4%E7%A7%9F-%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D2000%E6%AF%8F%E6%88%B65000%E5%85%83&h=f47b0b87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1750878/即時-港聞-周四起申請-渣打助劏房戶交租-名額2000每戶5000元</a><br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行今日宣布，將捐助社會服務聯會1000萬元，資助居於劏房的家庭在疫情期間支付租金。<br />\n<br />\n合資格的2000個家庭將每戶獲得一筆過5000元資助，金額與本港劏房戶於去年的每月租金中位數相若。資助將會在申請期完結後約1星期透過「轉數快」發放，以確保家庭可簡單及快捷地獲得資金，解決燃眉之急。"},{"pid":"e58a2f33ce80082251894696e20ef5d933e92782","tid":1980570,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"社聯將會管理和監督整個資助計畫，透過15個非政府機構服務單位於4月23日（本周四）至5月6日期間接受申請，成功申請人將於5月13日或之後陸續獲取資助金。社聯會於稍後直接向相關單位公布詳情。"},{"pid":"df6ecccb1e780cd167f436e8f37829b697469df8","tid":1980570,"uid":39470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"業主表示正呀喂 又可以加租"},{"pid":"7fb812ab5e8b4fb1bc7b022851d8af6cbccc2993","tid":1980570,"uid":42396,"lik