":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"有咩要求？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"社聯將會管理和監督整個租金資助計劃，透過15個非政府機構服務單位於4月23日至5月6日期間接受申請，申請人需符合以下條件：<br />\n<br />\n1. 疫症前家庭月入上限為全港家庭每月入息中位數的75%（4人家庭為32,625 元），及<br />\n2. 受疫症影響家庭收入減少30%或以上，及<br />\n3. 家庭成員包括 18 歲或以下的受養子女，及<br />\n4. 非綜援受助家庭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2622297/【新冠肺炎】渣打夥社聯推租金資助%202千劏房戶可獲一筆過5,000元【附申請資格】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2622297%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%A4%A5%E7%A4%BE%E8%81%AF%E6%8E%A8%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%25202%E5%8D%83%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%AF%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%86%E9%81%8E5%2C000%E5%85%83%E3%80%90%E9%99%84%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%91&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b210fdb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2622297/【新冠肺炎】渣打夥社聯推租金資助%202千劏房戶可獲一筆過5,000元【附申請資格】</a>"},{"pid":"c421eb0241a853eefe2229d48059652d1f4d60a6","tid":1980570,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"4. 非綜援受助家庭<br />\n呢點要執正黎做，班仆街成日扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"863acd7071905f5c2b3dd7f4539f63f46c945387","tid":1980570,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc27c902b183ff309ce7027bc1796bb048b2c14","tid":1980570,"uid":155674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"渣打如果係用FPS俾嘅話，算唔算一野ban落政府個頭度?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"相信無咩機構/國家<br />\n<br />\n會衰過港共"},{"pid":"d984023b453886afec00904e2c099fa31a1ec4e1","tid":1980570,"uid":295075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc27c902b183ff309ce7027bc1796bb048b2c14","tid":1980570,"uid":155674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"渣打如果係用FPS俾嘅話，算唔算一野ban落政府個頭度?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:09:57.00